modules.description: Processes DNS queries and constructs responses using strict protocol adherence. Operates on packet structures, domain names, and resource records. Implements recursive resolution and zone file parsing for network debugging and custom DNS configurations.

Handles DNS TSIG signature generation and verification using cryptographic keys and timestamps. Operates on DNS packets, cryptographic keys, domain names, and time values to ensure message integrity. Used to sign outgoing DNS responses and verify incoming signed DNS messages.
